highscores

Class GamePlayer

  • java.lang.Object
    • highscores.GamePlayer

  • public class GamePlayer
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represent a game player of Compounded. It is used to load and display the high scores. Total time spent: 1 hour.
    Version:
    1.0 May 18, 2014., 2.0 - No changes made., 3.0 - No changes made., 4.0 - No changes made., 5.0 - Mutator methods have been removed, since the state of GamePlayers will not need to be changed once it is created. The constructor with one parameter has been removed, since it is no longer necessary now that high scores has been implemented differently.
    Author:
    Joshua Yuan.
